# 🧬 Nuclei - Vulnerability Scanner
> **Fast and customizable vulnerability scanner based on simple YAML DSL.**

### 📥 Optimized Installation

**Option 1: Using Go (Standard Deployment)**
```bash
go install -v [github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei/v3/cmd/nuclei@latest](https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei/v3/cmd/nuclei@latest)

Option 2: Direct Binary Execution (Linux)
wget [https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei/releases/latest/download/nuclei_linux_amd64.zip](https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei/releases/latest/download/nuclei_linux_amd64.zip) && unzip nuclei_linux_amd64.zip && sudo mv nuclei /usr/local/bin/



🛠️ Execution Example
# Automated scanning against a target
nuclei -u [https://example.com](https://example.com)
